Package hu.bme.mit.theta.analysis

Class Trace<S,A>

java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.analysis.Trace<S,A>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cex
public final class Trace<S,A> extends Object implements Cex
Represents an immutable, alternating trace in the form of a (State, Action, State, ..., State, Action, State) sequence. A trace always contains at least one state and the number of actions is one less than the number of states.
